                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "Iframes are detected automatically during snapshots. When the main-frame snapshot runs, `Iframe` nodes are resolved and their content is inlined beneath the iframe element in the output (one level of nesting; iframes within iframes are not expanded)." ],
